## Challenge 1 - Saying Hello

### Goal
Create a program that prompts for your name and prints a greeting using your name

### Inputs
name

### Outputs
greetingMessage

### Pseudocode
Prompt for name with "What is your name?"

Concatentate name into greetingMessage "Hello name, nice to meet you!"

Display updated greetingMessage that includes name

### JS
```
function sayingHello() {
    var name = prompt("What is your name?");

    if(name) {
        var greetingMessage = "Hello " + name + ", nice to meet you!";
        alert(greetingMessage);
    } else {
        alert("I'm sorry? I didn't get your name.");
        sayingHello();
    }
}
```

