## Challenge 2 - Counting the Number of Characters

### Goal
Create a program that prompts for an input string and displays output that shows the input string and the number of characters the string contain

### Inputs
inputString

### Outputs
charCount

### Pseudocode
Prompt for inputString with "What is the input string?"

Count characters for inputString using built-in function

Display message with inputString and charCount - "inputString has charCount characters."

### JS
```
function stringCharCount() {
    var inputString = prompt("What is the input string?");
    if(inputString) {
        var charCount = inputString.length;
        alert(inputString + " has " + charCount + " characters.");
    } else {
        alert("String, please!");
        stringCharCount();
    }
}
```


