## Challenge 7 - Area of a Rectangular Room

### Goal
Create a program that calculates the area of a room. Prompt the user for the length and width of the room in feet. Then display the area in both square feet and square meters

### Inputs
roomLength
roomWidth

### Assumptions
conversionConstant = 0.09290304

### Outputs
areaSqft
areaSqm
confirmationMessage
finalMessage

### Pseudocode
Prompt for roomLength in feet with "What is the length of the room in feet?"
Prompt for roomWidth in feet with "What is the width of the room in feet?"

Declare conversionConstant

Convert roomLength to number format
convert roomWidth to number format

Calculate areaSqft with roomLength * roomWidth
Calculate areaSqm with areaSqft * conversionConstant and round to 3 decimal places

Concatenate confirmationMessage with "You entered dimensions of roomLength feet by roomWidth feet."
Concatenate finalMessage with "The area is (line break) areaSqft square feet (line break) areaSqm square meters"

Display confirmationMessage
Display finalMessage

### JS
```
function inputRoomLength () {
    var roomLength = prompt("What is the length of the room in feet?");

    if (!isNaN(roomLength) && (roomLength != "")) {
        roomLength = Number(roomLength);
        return roomLength;
    } else {
        alert("Submission invalid. Please try again! *beep boop*");
        inputRoomLength();
    }
}

function inputRoomWidth () {
    var roomWidth = prompt("What is the width of the room in feet?");

    if (!isNaN(roomWidth) && (roomWidth != "")) {
        roomWidth = Number(roomWidth);
        return roomWidth;
    } else {
        alert("Submission invalid. Please try again! *beep boop*");
        inputRoomWidth();
    }
}

function areaOfRectangularRoom() {
    var roomLength = inputRoomLength();
    var roomWidth = inputRoomWidth();

    var conversionConstant = 0.09290304;

    var areaSqft = roomLength * roomWidth;
	var areaSqm = parseFloat(areaSqft * conversionConstant).toFixed(3);

	var confirmationMessage = (`You entered dimensions of ${roomLength} feet by ${roomWidth} feet.`);

	var finalMessage = (`The area is\n${areaSqft} square feet\n${areaSqm} square meters`);

	alert(`${confirmationMessage}\n${finalMessage}`);
}
```

