## Challenge 8 - Pizza Party

### Goal
Write a program to evenly divide pizzas. Prompt for the number of people, the number of pizzas, and the number of slices per pizza. Ensure that the number of pieces comes out even. Display the number of pieces of pizza each person should get. If there are leftovers, show the number of leftover pieces

### Inputs
countPeople
countPizzas

### Assumptions
slicesPerPizza = 12?

### Outputs
slicesPerPerson
slicesLeftover
confirmationMessage
finalMessage

### Pseudocode
Prompt for countPeople with "How many people?"
Prompt for countPizzas with "How many pizzas do you have?"

Declare slicesPerPizza

Convert countPeople to number format
convert countPizzas to number format

Calculate totalSlices with countPizzas * slicesPerPizza
Calculate slicesPerPerson with totalSlices / countPeople, rounded down
Calculate slicesLeftover with totalSlices - (countPeople * slicesPerPerson)

Concatenate confirmationMessage with "countPeople people with countPizzas pizzas"
Concatenate finalMessage with "Each person gets slicesPerPerson slices of pizza. (line break) There are slicesLeftover leftover pieces."

Display confirmationMessage
Display finalMessage


